name: Beniksu Strawberry Kintamani
address: Jl. Raya Pujung, Batur Tengah, Kec. Kintamani, Kabupaten Bangli, Bali 80652, Indonesia
review 1: This is just a small farm along roadside, if you guys want to explore bigger farm, this is definitely not the right place. I have some difficulties to find this farm as theyâ€™re closing and no sign board. But somehow the strawberries taste sweet!
review 2: Very generous and kind people, must pop in and say hello
review 3: Travelled a long way for a stroberi farm and couldn't find it. No sign, and not where Google maps said.
review 4: Today go there no one on location asking the shop to find the owner after that just say close.

name: Galang Kangin hiking
address: P9F2+2P6, Jl. Raya Pujung, Batur Tengah, Kec. Kintamani, Kabupaten Bangli, Bali 80652, Indonesia
review 1: Driver was very fast to arrive at our airbnb to pick us up. The place also served us coffee/tea + pancake and staff were friendly! Everything was smooth and we had a good time :)
review 2:
very sweet crew. they served us coffee and pancakes for the pre trek breakfast.

they also packed a food basket for us with sandwiches and coffee that we had on the mountain top.

will highly recommend.
review 3: We had a fantastic experience with Galang Kangin Hiking during our hike on the top of Mt Batu and I would recommend to anyone who loves incredible sunrises to contact this company for the tour.
review 4: Collected from hotel at 2am and taken to a place to prepare, served coffee and pancake to build our strength. We were driven to the foot of the trail where we met out guide. Climb was harder than i was expecting but assistance was given when necessary. Glad to say we made it and watched the sun rise. Amazing adventure and these guys are the best.
review 5: I didnt come prepared. They offered sweaters which was nice. The guide was amazing and he offered to take pictures. View was amazing

review 2: Great cycle tour with volcanoes view
review 3: Great to stay a few night during in kintamani
